<h4>
  Please append all airports you have visited into the address/URL bar, after a '/' and seperate them with spaces.
</h4>
<h4>
  Valid Airport names can be found here:
</h4>
<ul>
  <li>
    <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IATA_airport_code">Wiki Link of IATA ( International Air Transport Association airport code) list</a>
  </li>
  <li>
    <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_airports_in_the_United_States">Wiki list of US airports</a>
  </li>
</ul>

<h4>
  Examples:
</h4>
<ul>
  <li>
    <h4>US airport codes</h4>
    <p>BHM --> Birmingham</p>
    <p>ANC --> Anchorage</p>
    <p>PHX --> Phoenix</p>
    <p>OAK --> Oakland</p>
    <p>DEN --> Denver</p>
    <p>ATL --> Atlanta</p>
    <p>HNL --> Honolulu</p>
    <p>ALB --> Albany</p>
    <p>BTV --> Burlington</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <h4>European airport codes</h4>
    <p>TXL --> Berlin, Germany</p>
    <p>LON --> London, United Kingdom</p>
    <p>ROM --> Rome, Italy</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <h4>Asian airport codes</h4>
    <p>JKT --> Jakarta, Indonesia</p>
    <p>HND --> Haneda Airport, Tokyo, Japan</p>
    <p>BKK --> Bangkok, Thailand</p>
  </li>
</ul>
